- 🔗 **Instant Connection**: One-tap connect with verified viewers
- 🏛️ **Governance Engagement**: Encourage real-time voting participation
- 👥 **Community Building**: Grow local Sentinel communities
- 🔒 **Privacy-First**: No user tracking, encrypted proximity data

