## 👥 Proximity-Based Discovery System

### User Discovery Flow

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│              USER DISCOVERY WORKFLOW                     │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

1. BEACON BROADCAST
   └─> User enables Bluetooth Nudges
   └─> App starts BLE beacon broadcasting
   └─> Encrypted user data transmitted

2. PROXIMITY DETECTION
   └─> BLE scanner detects nearby beacons
   └─> Distance calculated via RSSI
   └─> Beacon data decrypted and validated

3. USER MATCHING
   └─> Interest-based matching algorithm
   └─> Governance participation priority
   └─> Verification level weighting

4. NUDGE GENERATION
   └─> Priority score calculated
   └─> Nudge type determined
   └─> User notification created

5. USER ACTION
   └─> User views nudge
   └─> Takes action (connect, vote, engage)
   └─> Connection established via P2P network
```

### Matching Algorithm

```javascript
/**
 * Proximity Matching Algorithm
 * Calculates compatibility score between users
 */
function calculateCompatibilityScore(userA, userB, distance) {
  let score = 0;
  const maxScore = 100;
  
  // 1. Distance Score (0-30 points)
  // Closer = higher score
  if (distance < 5) score += 30;
  else if (distance < 10) score += 25;
  else if (distance < 20) score += 20;
  else if (distance < 50) score += 15;
  else score += 10;
  
  // 2. Interest Overlap (0-30 points)
  const commonInterests = userA.interests.filter(
    interest => userB.interests.includes(interest)
  );
  score += (commonInterests.length / Math.max(userA.interests.length, userB.interests.length)) * 30;
  
  // 3. Governance Participation (0-20 points)
  if (userA.governanceParticipation && userB.governanceParticipation) {
    score += 20;
  } else if (userA.governanceParticipation || userB.governanceParticipation) {
    score += 10;
  }
  
  // 4. Verification Level (0-20 points)
  const verificationScores = {
    'GOVERNANCE': 20,
    'PREMIUM': 15,
    'STANDARD': 10,
    'BASIC': 5,
    'UNVERIFIED': 0
  };
  score += (verificationScores[userA.verificationLevel] + 
            verificationScores[userB.verificationLevel]) / 2;
  
  return Math.min(score, maxScore);
}
```

